<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>The Bachelor's Bella Varelis put on a confident performance at Thursday night's cocktail party after receiving a rose from Locky Gilbert on their solo date.  </p>

<p>And it didn't take long before Irena Srbinovska, 31, found herself overwhelmed, fleeing the scene and breaking down in tears. </p>

<p>When she revealed her fears that Locky was 'slipping away' from her, hearts around the country broke for the mild-mannered nurse. It wasn't long before fans flocked to Twitter to share their upset.</p>

